title: Hamburg Bürgerschaft Elections
new-page: true
tags: event
priority: -2
view-if: (year = hamburg_election_year and month >= hamburg_election_month) or (year > hamburg_election_year)
on-departure: month_actions += 1; hamburg_election_year = hamburg_election_year + 4 if hamburg_snap_election_called == 0; hamburg_election_year = year + 4 if hamburg_snap_election_called == 1; hamburg_election_month = month if hamburg_snap_election_called == 1; hamburg_snap_election_called = 0
set-jump: hamburg_landtag_results

= Hamburg Bürgerschaft Elections, [+ month : month +] [+ year +]

Hamburg holds Bürgerschaft/Landtag elections. This system reuses the federal party-support system, applies Hamburg party weights, normalizes the result, and allocates **160** seats with D’Hondt.

- @calculate_hamburg_landtag: Count the votes.

@calculate_hamburg_landtag
on-arrival: hamburg_government = 3 if hamburg_government == undefined; hamburg_leader = "Rudolf Ross" if hamburg_leader == undefined; hamburg_majority_cabinet = 1 if hamburg_majority_cabinet == undefined
go-to: election_algorithm
set-jump: hamburg_landtag_results

@hamburg_landtag_results
on-arrival: {! var isHamburgSnapElection = Number(Q.hamburg_snap_election_called) === 1; Q.hamburg_next_election_year_preview = (isHamburgSnapElection ? (Number(Q.year) || 0) : (Number(Q.hamburg_election_year) || Number(Q.year) || 0)) + 4; Q.hamburg_next_election_month_preview = isHamburgSnapElection ? Q.month : Q.hamburg_election_month; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.calculateHamburgLandtagResults === 'function') { window.calculateHamburgLandtagResults(Q); } !}

= Hamburg Bürgerschaft election results

Next Hamburg election after this Bürgerschaft is due in **[+ hamburg_next_election_month_preview : month +] [+ hamburg_next_election_year_preview +]**.

Hamburg Bürgerschaft seats: **[+ hamburg_landtag_total_seats +] / 160**

Current Hamburg government: **[+ hamburg_current_government_name +]** ([+ hamburg_current_government_parties +]) led by **[+ hamburg_leader +]**.

Current government seats: **[+ hamburg_current_government_seats +] / 160**. Status: **[+ hamburg_current_government_status +]**. Majority cabinet: **[+ hamburg_majority_cabinet +]**.

