{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#8B0000'> </div> !} KPD{!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_kpd_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_kpd_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#DCCA4A'> </div> !} [+ ddp_name +]{!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_ddp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_ddp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#D5AC27'> </div> !} DVP{!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_dvp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_dvp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#3f7bc1'> </div> !} DNVP{!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_dnvp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_dnvp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#000'> </div> !} Z{!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_z_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_z_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#954B00'> </div> !} NSDAP{!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_nsdap_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_nsdap_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td><div class="box" style='background-color:#7A5C20'> </div> !} WP{!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_wp_votes_disp +]% {!</td><td>!} [+ hamburg_wp_r +] {!</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}

= Choose a Hamburg coalition

A coalition is selectable if it controls at least **81** of the **160** Bürgerschaft seats. If no listed coalition has a majority, the incumbent Hamburg government may continue as a minority cabinet.

- @hamburg_select_spd_kpd
- @hamburg_select_sole_spd
- @hamburg_select_spd_ddp
- @hamburg_select_spd_ddp_dvp
- @hamburg_select_ddp_dnvp_wp_dvp
- @new_hamburg_elections: Call new Hamburg Bürgerschaft elections.
- @root: Continue without changing the Hamburg government.

@hamburg_select_spd_kpd
title: SPD-KPD
subtitle: SPD + KPD — [+ hamburg_spd_kpd_coalition_seats +] / 160 — [+ hamburg_spd_kpd_coalition_status +]
view-if: hamburg_spd_kpd_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.hamburg_government = 1; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: hamburg_leader_selection

@hamburg_select_sole_spd
title: Sole SPD
subtitle: SPD — [+ hamburg_sole_spd_coalition_seats +] / 160 — [+ hamburg_sole_spd_coalition_status +]
view-if: hamburg_sole_spd_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.hamburg_government = 2; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: hamburg_leader_selection

@hamburg_select_spd_ddp
title: SPD-DDP
subtitle: SPD + DDP — [+ hamburg_spd_ddp_coalition_seats +] / 160 — [+ hamburg_spd_ddp_coalition_status +]
view-if: hamburg_spd_ddp_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.hamburg_government = 3; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: hamburg_leader_selection

@hamburg_select_spd_ddp_dvp
title: SPD-DDP-DVP
subtitle: SPD + DDP + DVP — [+ hamburg_spd_ddp_dvp_coalition_seats +] / 160 — [+ hamburg_spd_ddp_dvp_coalition_status +]
view-if: hamburg_spd_ddp_dvp_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.hamburg_government = 4; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: hamburg_leader_selection

@hamburg_select_ddp_dnvp_wp_dvp
title: DDP-DNVP-WP-DVP
subtitle: DDP + DNVP + WP + DVP — [+ hamburg_ddp_dnvp_wp_dvp_coalition_seats +] / 160 — [+ hamburg_ddp_dnvp_wp_dvp_coalition_status +]
view-if: hamburg_ddp_dnvp_wp_dvp_coalition_selectable = 1
on-arrival: {! Q.hamburg_government = 5; if (typeof window !== 'undefined' && typeof window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions === 'function') { window.updateHamburgCoalitionOptions(Q); } !}
go-to: hamburg_leader_selection

@new_hamburg_elections
title: Call new Hamburg Bürgerschaft elections.
on-arrival: hamburg_election_year = year; hamburg_election_month = month; hamburg_snap_election_called = 1
go-to: calculate_hamburg_landtag

@hamburg_leader_selection

= Choose the Hamburg leader

Selected coalition: **[+ hamburg_current_government_name +]** ([+ hamburg_current_government_parties +]).

Coalition seats: **[+ hamburg_current_government_seats +] / 160**. Status: **[+ hamburg_current_government_status +]**.

- @hamburg_leader_ross
- @hamburg_leader_petersen
- @hamburg_leader_dauch

@hamburg_leader_ross
title: Rudolf Ross
subtitle: Available because the SPD is in the Hamburg cabinet.
view-if: hamburg_government = 1 or hamburg_government = 2 or hamburg_government = 3 or hamburg_government = 4
on-arrival: hamburg_leader = "Rudolf Ross"
go-to: hamburg_government_confirmed

@hamburg_leader_petersen
title: Carl Wilhelm Petersen
subtitle: Available because the DDP is in the Hamburg cabinet and the SPD is not.
view-if: hamburg_government = 5
on-arrival: hamburg_leader = "Carl Wilhelm Petersen"
go-to: hamburg_government_confirmed

@hamburg_leader_dauch
title: Walther Dauch
subtitle: Fallback DVP leader for a Hamburg cabinet without the SPD or DDP.
view-if: hamburg_government = 0
on-arrival: hamburg_leader = "Walther Dauch"
go-to: hamburg_government_confirmed

@hamburg_government_confirmed

